comment: Conjectured to be a permutation of the natural numbers.

mathematica: max = 57; f = True; a = {1, 3, 5}; NN = Range[4, 1000]; s = 2*NN - 1; While[TrueQ[f], For[k = 1, k <= Length[s], k++, If[Length[a] < max, If[GCD[a[[-1]], s[[k]]] == 1 && GCD[a[[-2]], s[[k]]] > 1, a = Append[a, s[[k]]]; s = Delete[s, k]; k = 0; Break], f = False]]]; Table[(a[[n]] + 1)/2, {n, max}] (* _L.
